Puppet playground

Simple test setup of an puppet master and agent to test modules in a virtual environment.
Puppet nodes are self-classifying (http://nuknad.com/2011/02/11/self-classifying-puppet-nodes/)
check out scripts/setup-puppet-agent-web.sh


Requirements:
- ruby
- virtualbox
- vagrant

Run:
- vagrant up
- vagrant ssh puppetmaster
- vagrant ssh puppetagent_app
- vagrant ssh puppetagent_memcached
- vagrant ssh puppetagent_web
http://localhost:8080 -> http://puppetagent_web:80
